<p>&#8216;Updated sentencing guidelines for animal cruelty offences that reflect changes introduced by the Animal Welfare (Sentencing) Act 2021, were published today by the Sentencing Council following consultation.&#8217;</p>
<p><a href="https://www.sentencingcouncil.org.uk/news/item/animal-cruelty-offences-new-sentencing-guidelines-published/">Full Story</a></p><p>Sentencing Council, 10th May 2023</p><p>Source: <a href="https://www.sentencingcouncil.org.uk">www.sentencingcouncil.org.uk</a></p>